{"tid":509870,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"致：港豬，中国同胞","createTime":"2017-12-25T19:17:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-25T19:17:49.000Z","uid":46781,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"17d10336dc493e2d68db386c9c128a7ac5e09de5","tid":509870,"uid":46781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T19:17:49.000Z","msg":"啱啱喺facebook睇到呢張圖<br />\n<br />\n簡潔又有力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/26/025835_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F26%2F025835_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=4488fa68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位中国同胞唔好俾人睇死！要話俾香港人知我地幾愛中国！<br />\n希望日後喜歡中国共产党嘅人，一齊返去偉大祖國嘅懷抱啦，唔好再口裡說不，身體卻很誠實！<br />\n<br />\n企硬！向單雙程證說<strong>不</strong>，向公屋說<strong>不</strong>，向綜援說<strong>不</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>相信</strong>中国嘅醫療，食物，相信党！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">邊個留喺香港就係背叛党，我地實會向党告發你！</span></span></strong>"}]}